{"tid":474450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球第一個海上漂浮國家將在2020面世","createTime":"2017-11-20T07:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T10:46:18.000Z","uid":63669,"like":187,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"3b46171c4779721e0c674f3752ede83ca5880264","tid":474450,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:22:55.000Z","msg":"要在不打仗不公投獨立的情況下建立一個國家，現在真的談何容易，不過預計在 2020 年，就會有一個全新的國家出現，而且還是漂浮在太平洋大溪地對出的公海，擁有自己的法律和獨立運作。這是由 PayPal 創辦人 Peter Thiel 提供資金支持，於太平洋公海興建漂浮城市項目的構想。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1120-1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F1120-1a.jpg&h=3508feee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n非牟利組織 Seasteading Institute 會在漂浮城市興建住宅、辦公區、酒店、餐廳等，讓進駐的「國民」可以在一個全新的政治生態和法律下生活，而相關法律會在明年開始起草。透過這座漂浮城市，Seasteading Institute 希望能夠做到在海洋取得食物自給自足，進行病患治療，達到淨化大氣層，甚至讓窮人獲得財富等目標。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1120-1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F1120-1b.jpg&h=bb87f90d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n所以這座將會在 2019 年動工興建的漂浮城市，會有水產養殖農場、醫療保健和研究的設施和可持續使用發電站，以達成上述目標。這只是 Seasteading Institute 的第一座漂浮城市，未來還會興建更多，再按照國民的需要在重新排列，令他們的生活更便捷和美好。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/1120-1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F1120-1c.jpg&h=772df993&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8df33069af8daba6439d776cea39668e155f1ccf","tid":474450,"uid":57835,"like":76,"dislike":2,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"Idealism"},{"pid":"4250186ca0c349e328b66bf7f83e8607b5c15fdb","tid":474450,"uid":59929,"like":73,"dislike":10,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T07:24:53.000Z","msg":"以為2020開始有人住係垃圾上面"},{"pid":"11c049e4144ffdd1ca0db62bdde6fd8b9fe5e2ce